t=\"\" width=\"36\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/u6uA7Yo.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/wm2UCet.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/Cw074li.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"36\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/2j5X6pZ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/DXcKlJf.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/vTsTyrz.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/mQgIVDu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/5xXqhXe.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/kVHzJV9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/cYHSkb2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/GuGTe3L.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/5EiwS3H.png\" width=\"253\" height=\"40\" /><br /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/aHc4S93.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/aK7ykEb.png\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/pwwoJoz.png\" width=\"35\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/uvtNHb5.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/VYJzkYE.png\" width=\"51\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/sKvQO1d.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/0bzO6jP.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/IyD3iA5.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/JmLbhkJ.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/UWFTH8U.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/xihe1Iq.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/mttOKJb.png\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/8U6EqW7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/EY1Banv.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"35\" height=\"26\" /><img src=\"https://imgur.com/pRShE0c.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"26\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/1h9o2Kx.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"838\" height=\"34\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Just Potion Rings is a mod inspired in <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/potion-fingers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Potion Fingers</a>, the mod create every mob effect into a ring,</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">even if you install a mod&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">who adds more effects Just Potion Rings will&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">add more rings with the new mob effects&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">See the wiki for:</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/Dplayend/Just-Potion-Rings/wiki/Recipes\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Recipes</a> / <a href=\"https://github.com/Dplayend/Just-Potion-Rings/wiki/LootChest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">LootChest</a> /&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Dplayend/Just-Potion-Rings/wiki/Trades\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Trades</a> /&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Dplayend/Just-Potion-Rings/wiki/Commands\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Commands</a> / <a href=\"https://github.com/Dplayend/Just-Potion-Rings/wiki#compatibility\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Compatibility</a>&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/Dplayend/Just-Potion-Rings/wiki/Datapack#how-to-create-a-ring-recipe\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">How to make Ring recipes via Datapack</a></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/nNw9qcQ.gif\" width=\"413\" height=\"233\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hEo18QI.gif\" width=\"413\" height=\"233\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://imgur.com/1h9o2Kx.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"838\" height=\"34\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>F.A.Q.s</strong></span></em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Q: Can I include Just Potion Rings in my mod pack?</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">A: Sure, just put my mod in the related projects<br /><strong>Q: How many rings can I obtain in vanilla experience?</strong><br />A: Only 13 rings are obtainable in vanilla experience. see the <a href=\"https://github.com/Dplayend/Just-Potion-Rings/wiki\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">wiki</a> for the recipes and other ways to obtains rings</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Q: Why the version Forge 1.21.x of Just Potion Rings is not available?</strong><br />A: There is no version of Curios 1.21.x yet, you can see the reason <a href=\"https://github.com/TheIllusiveC4/Curios/issues/427\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Q: How can i made more recipes for other potion effects, it works with mod potion effect?</strong><br />A: You can make recipes via datapack, see the <a href=\"Q: Why the version Forge 1.21.x of Just Potion Rings is not available? A: There is no version of Curios 1.21.x yet, you can see the reason here.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">wiki</a> to know how to make it and yes it works with potion effects created by mods</span></p>",
